   some degree this designation is arbitary.  They come from a variety of
   sources, as noted below.  Please see the packages utile-1.0.src.tar.Z
   (utile10.taz) and utila-1.2.src.tar.Z (utila12.taz) for utilities which
   "belong" in /etc and /usr/bin, respectively.

